content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 21 ยง 1261.32 - Gross weight of aircraft using Newark Airport restricted

State Regulations

No aircraft on a dual tandem gear having an actual
gross weight of over 300,000 pounds, including passengers, cargo, fuel, equipment, etc., shall land, take off or taxi at Newark Airport without
permission. Notes
